'''''Sambizanga''''' ni film yo mu 1972 yakozwe n'umuyobozi Sarah Maldoror<ref>Sambizanga (filmlinc.org)</ref> . yashyizweho mu 1961 igihe Intambara y’Ubwigenge ya Angola yatangiraga<ref>Buy tickets for Sambizanga | BFI London Film Festival 2021 <nowiki>https://whatson.bfi.org.uk</nowiki> › lff › Online › BOparam::W...</ref>, ikurikira urugamba rw’abarwanyi ba Angola bagize uruhare mu ishyaka rya rubanda riharanira kwibohora muri Angola (MPLA)<ref>Sambizanga. 1972. Directed by Sarah Maldoror | MoMA <nowiki>https://www.moma.org</nowiki> › calendar › events</ref>, umutwe wa politiki urwanya ubukoloni umugabo wa Maldoror<ref>' Sambizanga,' New Film About Angola, Tells of Oppression ... <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 1973/11/22 › archives › samb...</ref>, Mário Coelho Pinto de Andrade, yari umuyobozi. Iyi filime ishingiye ku gitabo cyitwa ''A vida verdadeira de Domingos Xavier'' ("Ubuzima nyabwo bwa Domingos Xavier") cyanditswe n'umwanditsi wa Angola, José Luandino Vieira<ref>Screen: Sambizanga, Xala, and Kongi's Harvest - jstor <nowiki>https://www.jstor.org</nowiki> › stable</ref> .

== Umusaruro ==
Iyi filime yafatiwe ahantu muri Repubulika y’abaturage ya Kongo (izwi kandi nka Congo-Brazzaville) mu byumweru birindwi<ref>Africa | Outrage at Angola actor shooting - BBC NEWS <nowiki>http://news.bbc.co.uk</nowiki> › africa</ref>. 

== Abakinnyi ==
Benshi mu bakinnyi bari abadafite umwuga bagize uruhare mu bikorwa bimwe na bimwe byo muri Afurika birwanya ubukoloni<ref>Cinema and the Anticolonial Liberation Struggles: Sambizanga <nowiki>https://www.nottinghamcontemporary.org</nowiki> › whats-on</ref>, nka MPLA n’ishyaka nyafurika riharanira ubwigenge bwa Gineya na Cape Verde (PAIGC)<ref>Sambizanga (1972) awards & festivals on MUBI</ref>.  Imiterere ya Domingos Xavier yakinwe n'umuny'Angola uba muri Kongo, Domingos Oliveira naho imico ya Maria yakinwe n’umuhanga mu bukungu Elisa Andrade ukomoka muri [[Kapu Veri|Cape Verde]]<ref>Cape Verdean labourers, settlers and emigrants | BUALA</ref> 

